  "code": "sequenceDiagram\n    participant A as Computadora A<br/>(Groupware_WikiPage)\n    participant S as Switch<br/>(Groupware_SprintBacklog)\n    participant B as Computadora B<br/>(Groupware_ChatRoom)\n    participant C as Computadora C<br/>(Groupware_SprintBacklog)\n    participant D as Computadora D<br/>(Groupware_WikiPage)\n\n    Note over S: Tabla MAC vacía\n\n    Note over A,D: FASE 1: ARP Request (Groupware_ChatRoom)\n    \n    A->>S: ARP Request<br/>Origen: A (Groupware_WikiPage)<br/>Destino: Broadcast (Groupware_IssueTracker)\n    \n    Note over S: Aprende: Puerto 1 → MAC de A\n    \n    S->>B: ARP Request (Groupware_IssueTracker)\n    S->>C: ARP Request (Groupware_ChatRoom)\n    S->>D: ARP Request (Groupware_ChatRoom)\n    \n    Note over B,D: Solo C responde al ARP\n\n    Note over A,D: FASE 2: ARP Response\n    \n    C->>S: ARP Response<br/>Origen: C (Groupware_KanbanBoard)<br/>Destino: A (Groupware_KanbanBoard)\n    \n    Note over S: Aprende: Puerto 3 → MAC de C\n    \n    S->>A: ARP Response (Groupware_ChatRoom)\n\n    Note over A,D: FASE 3: Comunicación Directa\n    \n    A->>S: Datos para C<br/>Origen: A (Groupware_KanbanBoard)<br/>Destino: C (Groupware_ChatRoom)\n    \n    Note over S: Consulta tabla MAC<br/>Encuentra C en puerto 3\n    \n    S->>C: Datos (Groupware_WikiPage)",
