  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个ARP协议在Groupware环境下的序列图，展示四台电脑通过交换机通信的过程。核心是要体现Groupware工具如何映射到网络层的行为。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "Computadora B",
        "Computadora C",
        "Computadora D",
        "Switch",
        "ARP"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我初步设想让每台电脑绑定一个Groupware工具，比如WikiPage、ChatRoom这些。交换机对应SprintBacklog作为协调中心。这样工具和网络角色的对应关系会更清晰，您看方向对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_WikiPage",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom",
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog",
        "Switch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，这个映射很好。A和D用WikiPage，B用ChatRoom，C和交换机都用SprintBacklog。这样C既是参与者又是 backlog 的镜像，能体现分布式协作的冗余感。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "Computadora D",
        "Groupware_WikiPage",
        "Computadora B",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom",
        "Computadora C",
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出五个参与者：A(WikiPage)、B(ChatRoom)、C(SprintBacklog)、D(WikiPage)，以及交换机S(SprintBacklog)。初始状态我在交换机上方加一个注释，标注MAC表为空。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "Note over S",
        "Tabla MAC vacía"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来进入第一阶段：ARP请求。A想要找C，但不知道C的MAC地址，所以发广播。这里我想用Groupware_ChatRoom来标记这个广播行为，因为广播就像群发消息。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "ARP Request",
        "Broadcast",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "广播的目标用Groupware_IssueTracker会不会更合适？IssueTracker通常是全员可见的公共面板，而ChatRoom更像是会话。或者您希望ChatRoom贯穿整个发现过程？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_IssueTracker",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom",
        "Broadcast"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有道理，广播用IssueTracker，响应阶段再用ChatRoom。这样ARP Request从A到S，标注源是A(WikiPage)，目标是Broadcast(IssueTracker)。然后S学习A的MAC，记录在端口1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ARP Request",
        "Groupware_WikiPage",
        "Groupware_IssueTracker",
        "Switch",
        "Puerto 1",
        "MAC de A"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：A到S的ARP Request，带源和目的标注。交换机学习后在旁边加了注释\"Aprende: Puerto 1 → MAC de A\"。现在S要把广播转发给B、C、D三条线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A-S",
        "S-B",
        "S-C",
        "S-D",
        "ARP Request"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，三条转发的Groupware标注需要区分一下。B那边保持IssueTracker，因为B不是目标只是旁听；C和D用ChatRoom，暗示它们可能进入对话状态。这样后续只有C响应的逻辑更顺。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S-B",
        "Groupware_IssueTracker",
        "S-C",
        "S-D",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我调整一下。刚才三条线都准备用IssueTracker，现在改成：S→B用IssueTracker，S→C和S→D用ChatRoom。然后在B和D上方加注释说明只有C会响应。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S-B",
        "S-C",
        "S-D",
        "Groupware_IssueTracker",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom",
        "Note over B,D"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美。现在进入第二阶段ARP响应。C知道自己是目标，直接单播回复给A。这里源和目的都用Groupware_KanbanBoard，因为Kanban的卡片移动很像定向的任务回执。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ARP Response",
        "Computadora C",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Computadora A"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已画C到S的ARP Response，标注源C(KanbanBoard)、目的A(KanbanBoard)。交换机再次学习，记录端口3对应C的MAC。然后S转发给A，这条线用ChatRoom？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C-S",
        "ARP Response",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Note over S",
        "Puerto 3",
        "MAC de C",
        "S-A"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，S到A的响应用ChatRoom，这样和第一阶段的广播形成对比：广播是IssueTracker的公共张贴，响应是ChatRoom的私密回话。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S-A",
        "ARP Response",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "第二阶段完成。现在进入第三阶段直接通信。A要给C发数据，这时候交换机已经知道C在端口3，可以直接转发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FASE 3",
        "Comunicación Directa",
        "A-S",
        "Datos para C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "数据包的标注我想换一下：源用Groupware_KanbanBoard，目的用Groupware_ChatRoom。体现A把任务卡片(Kanban)推给C，C在会话(ChatRoom)中接收。和之前的KanbanBoard用法形成语义上的呼应但角色互换。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Datos para C",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom",
        "Origen",
        "Destino"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "有意思，ARP响应时C是源KanbanBoard，现在A是源KanbanBoard。那交换机转发给C的时候，这条数据线用什么标注？保持WikiPage让工具类型更丰富，还是延续ChatRoom？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S-C",
        "Datos",
        "Groupware_WikiPage",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "用WikiPage。这样整个图里WikiPage出现在A、D的静态角色和数据传输的最终落地，形成闭环。而且WikiPage的持久存储特性很适合表示数据最终到达目的地的状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S-C",
        "Datos",
        "Groupware_WikiPage",
        "Computadora C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：A到S的数据包，源KanbanBoard、目的ChatRoom；交换机查询MAC表找到C在端口3的注释；S到C的数据线标注WikiPage。整个流程应该完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A-S",
        "Datos para C",
        "Note over S",
        "Consulta tabla MAC",
        "Encuentra C en puerto 3",
        "S-C",
        "Groupware_WikiPage"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我检查一下各阶段的注释。第一阶段是\"FASE 1: ARP Request (Groupware_ChatRoom)\"，但ChatRoom其实是第二阶段才主要用的。这里是不是该改成IssueTracker？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FASE 1",
        "ARP Request",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom",
        "Groupware_IssueTracker",
        "Note over A,D"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "您说得对，阶段注释应该和该阶段的核心工具一致。我把第一阶段的标注改成IssueTracker，第二阶段保持ChatRoom，第三阶段不需要额外标注。同时修正了拼写，确保所有Groupware名称准确。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FASE 1",
        "Groupware_IssueTracker",
        "FASE 2",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom",
        "Note over A,D"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "很好。再确认一下D的角色——D在图中只作为ARP请求的接收方出现，但没有响应也没有后续数据交互。这个静默设计是故意的，用来对比C的活跃参与。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora D",
        "Groupware_WikiPage",
        "ARP Request",
        "S-D"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，D收到广播但不响应，符合ARP协议中只有目标IP匹配的机器才回复的规则。D的WikiPage角色也暗示它是文档存储节点，不主动参与即时协作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora D",
        "Groupware_WikiPage",
        "Note over B,D",
        "Solo C responde al ARP"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 23,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后一个小调整：交换机S的SprintBacklog标注，在初始参与者声明里已经写了，但所有经过S的消息其实都在体现backlog的协调功能。不需要额外修改，只是确认这个隐喻是自洽的。",
      "elements_involved": [
